parameters:
Kru: "No way, what's up with this forest... It's so vast and the climb is
exhausting..."

Kru: "Phew... But did all those who didn't return die in this forest? There
aren't any monsters strong enough to kill..."

Kru: "Well, it's about obtaining immortality. It wouldn't be worth it if
the trial wasn't proportionate..."
Kru: "But immortality, huh... Do I really want to live that long..."
Kru: "A girl's voice No way In the depths of the forest like this"
Kru: "Anyway, I've got to go help"
This is the place where I first met Kru...
That day, I entered the Sacred Forest searching for the missing Mii-A...
Even though she hadn't actually gone missing...
And then, finding Kru, my destiny changed...
Since then, so many things have happened...
Umi: "I wonder... was it good for Kru to have met Umi...?"
If I hadn't met Kru at this place on that day...
Maybe Kru could have lived without suffering...
I can't help but think such things...
??? "The two of them were destined to meet..."
??? "That is something that cannot be changed..."
??? "But there are things that can be changed"

??? "There must be hope... as long as there is a strong heart to face it,
there must be..."

??? "Don't forget the precious feelings you hold, Umi... believe in...
fate..."
